'''StatCounter'''是一個[[網站流量|網站流量]]分析工具，主要提供[[網頁瀏覽器的使用分佈|網頁瀏覽器的使用分佈]]的訊息，其中包括免費的基本方案與付費的進階服務，價格分別為5[[美元|美元]]與119美元/月<ref name="Twitter for Dummies">{{Cite book|title = Twitter Marketing for Dummies|url = https://archive.org/details/twittermarketing0000lacy|series = --For Dummies|publisher = [[John_Wiley_&_Sons|John Wiley & Sons]]|location = [[Hoboken,_New_Jersey|Hoboken, New Jersey]]|author = Lacy, Kyle|page = [https://archive.org/details/twittermarketing0000lacy/page/93 93]|year = 2011|isbn = 9780470930571}}</ref>。StatCounter的總部位於[[都柏林|都柏林]]<ref name="statcounterglobal">{{Cite web|url = http://gs.statcounter.com/|title = StatCounter Global Stats|publisher = StatCounter|accessdate = 22 August 2012|archive-date = 2012-05-26|archive-url = https://archive.is/20120526/http://gs.statcounter.com/%23mobile_browser-ww-monthly-201012-201111-bar}}</ref>，另外StatCounter約被3%的網站所採用<ref name="w3techusage">{{Cite web|title = Usage statistics and market share of StatCounter for websites|url = http://w3techs.com/technologies/details/ta-statcounter/all/all|website = W3Techs|publisher = Q-Success|accessdate = 8 January 2015|archive-date = 2019-05-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190526190033/https://w3techs.com/technologies/details/ta-statcounter/all/all}}</ref>。

Statcounter從300萬個網站中獲得每個月約150億次的點擊量來做網路分析<ref name="faqmethod">{{cite web | url=http://gs.statcounter.com/faq#methodology | title=FAQ | at=What methodology is used to calculate StatCounter Global Stats? | publisher=StatCounter | accessdate=8 January 2015 | archive-date=2012-12-14 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6CuNamGWK?url=http://gs.statcounter.com/faq#methodology | dead-url=no }}</ref>。沒有經過權重的校正來排除[[以偏概全|以偏概全]]的問題造成其數據的代表性不足。<br>

網站由奧德罕·卡倫在16歲時創立，並且擔任StatCounter[[執行長|執行長]]一執至今，隨後在2008年獲得了金蜘蛛獎的'''網路英雄'''這個獎項<ref>{{cite news | work=TechCentral.ie | publisher=[[ComputerScope#MediaTeam|MediaTeam]] | date=21 November 2008 | url=http://www.techcentral.ie/article.aspx?id=12820 | title=eircom Golden Spiders announced | deadurl=yes | archivedate=2010-11-19 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101119064451/http://www.techcentral.ie/article.aspx?id=12820 | accessdate=2015-10-17 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.leemunroe.com/golden-spider-awards-2008-winners/ | at=Internet Hero | accessdate=8 January 2015 | title=Golden Spider Awards 2008 Winners | date=November 2008 | author=Munroe, Lee | type=blog | archive-date=2016-03-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303225334/http://www.leemunroe.com/golden-spider-awards-2008-winners/ | dead-url=yes }}</ref>，也獲得了2007年[[彭博商業周刊|彭博商業周刊]]'''年輕歐洲年度企業家'''這一項殊榮<ref>{{cite news | author=Reinhardt, Andy | author2=Schenker, Jennifer L. | title=Europe's Young Entrepreneurs 2007 | department=Global Economics | work=[[Bloomberg_Businessweek|Bloomberg Businessweek]] | date=1 June 2007 | url=http://www.businessweek.com/stories/2007-06-01/europes-young-entrepreneurs-2007businessweek-business-news-stock-market-and-financial-advice | accessdate=2015-10-17 | archive-date=2015-01-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150117223442/http://www.businessweek.com/stories/2007-06-01/europes-young-entrepreneurs-2007businessweek-business-news-stock-market-and-financial-advice | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconrepublic.com/careers/item/8521-the-friday-interview-aodha|title=The Friday interview: Aodhan Cullen, StatCounter|author=John Kennedy|publisher=siliconrepublic.com|date=2007-08-03|accessdate=2012-09-21|archive-date=2012-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121019193925/http://www.siliconrepublic.com/careers/item/8521-the-friday-interview-aodha|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

